dependencies required on auto-scaler pod
-----------------------------------------
1. python version >= 3.5 - apt-get update; apt-get install python3.5 -y
2. nano editor - apt-get install nano
3. pip - apt-get install python-pip
	 apt-get install python3-pip -y
4. python packages
	a. numpy - pip3 install numpy
	b. requests - pip3 install requests
	#additional for baysian auto-scaler
	c. sklearn - pip3 install sklearn
	d. matplotlib - pip3 install matplotlib
